{"word":"G3618 - οἰκοδομέω - oikodoméō - oy-kod-om-eh'-o - Build","slug":"G3618","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">οἰκοδομέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>oikodoméō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>oy-kod-om-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Build"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BF;&#x03B9;&#x0313;&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x03B4;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - oikodomeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>oy-kod-om-eh'-o</i><p/>From the same as <a href=\"#/G3619\">G3619</a>; to <i>be</i> a <i>house builder</i>, that is, <i>construct</i> or (figuratively) <i>confirm:</i> - (be in) build (-er, -ing, up), edify, embolden."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2026\">G2026</a>, <a href=\"#/G2731\">G2731</a>, <a href=\"#/G2732\">G2732</a>, <a href=\"#/G2733\">G2733</a>, <a href=\"#/G3609\">G3609</a>, <a href=\"#/G3611\">G3611</a>, <a href=\"#/G3613\">G3613</a>, <a href=\"#/G3614\">G3614</a>, <a href=\"#/G3615\">G3615</a>, <a href=\"#/G3616\">G3616</a>, <a href=\"#/G3617\">G3617</a>, <a href=\"#/G3619\">G3619</a>, <a href=\"#/G3620\">G3620</a>, <a href=\"#/G3621\">G3621</a>, <a href=\"#/G3622\">G3622</a>, <a href=\"#/G3623\">G3623</a>, <a href=\"#/G3624\">G3624</a>, <a href=\"#/G4925\">G4925</a>"}]}